{"tid":1430600,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JS2020]浸大文院新生入","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:26:20.000Z","uid":276382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"443749021c57d1a6c1067f418dd42f5565327e8c","tid":1430600,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:12:08.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入文院大家庭！<br />\n如果你係巴打，恭喜你，因為文院好多女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知聽日罷reg會唔會影響到你地。<br />\n有乜嘢reg科、reg hall etc 嘅問題都可以問。<br />\n老鬼們都入黎識下學妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 首先推個page</span></strong><br />\nHKBU Freshman info：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkbufreshmaninfo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkbufreshmaninfo%2F&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=2077d6dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkbufreshmaninfo/</a><br />\n呢個page好有用，有各項重要日子提醒。<br />\n樓主到依家都成日靠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小編好好人，基本上係有問必答。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 關於Reg科</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.1 咩叫Reg科？</span></strong><br />\nReg 科即係Course Pre-registration。<br />\n係比你揀今個sem讀咩科嘅機會。<br />\n當然唔係任你揀啦，下面會講下有咩必修科同選修課。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2.2 幾時Reg科？</strong></span><br />\n今年yr 1 嘅reg科日子係8月14-16日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwphiYm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwphiYm.jpg&h=bfe3bb36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於學校server廢，需要分流。<br />\n所以每個人嘅reg科時段<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">是不同的</span></span>。<br />\n記得攞到BUniPort（類似內聯網） account後要入 Studies 》Registration 》Pre-registration 睇左自己所屬時段先呀！<br />\n錯過左就冇書讀架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2.3 要Reg咩科？</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9WjxrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9WjxrX.jpg&h=d6fba469&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nBU有樣好19嘅嘢叫GE(general education)。<br />\n除左其他U會有嘅大中大英，會逼你讀PE、其他院嘅course、數哲史。讀曬先grad到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文院Yr 1因為仲未揀major，所以今年讀嘅都會係GE course。<br />\n上面張圖只係講左你4年入面要讀咩先grad到。<br />\n至於今個sem要讀咩科，同埋要讀幾多cred，就要去 Studies》Study Progression》My Study Schedule 入面睇。<br />\n<br />\n不過未必要跟足schedule嘅。<br />\n科同科可能會time crush，<br />\n亦有可能抽唔中，<br />\n總之四年入面讀曬就ok。<br />\n<br />\n最最重要，記得諗定想讀咩科+排好時間表先！<br />\n<br />\n睇上堂時間：去Studies 》Programmes &amp; Courses Information 》Course Information<br />\n睇會教咩：喺Course Information入面，㩒Course Title，就會彈syllabus出黎㗎喇！<br />\n重點黎喇，如果想過三爆四，就一定要參考呢份Reg科攻略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B7BvLKzICgBnusgDYfi0BGWnxypEjLL89k_SXT8D6yU/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1B7BvLKzICgBnusgDYfi0BGWnxypEjLL89k_SXT8D6yU%2Fhtmlview&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=a1b798e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B7BvLKzICgBnusgDYfi0BGWnxypEjLL89k_SXT8D6yU/htmlview</a><br />\n入面有唔同course嘅comment，幫你避開killer，輕鬆靚grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果完左sem想警惕後人/推薦神course，呢邊請：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfmmEvZT7l2RZzD_Y1tIIVEasAL_p3QVkuLb-_FKe_2SKiLMQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfmmEvZT7l2RZzD_Y1tIIVEasAL_p3QVkuLb-_FKe_2SKiLMQ%2Fviewform&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=db43e21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfmmEvZT7l2RZzD_Y1tIIVEasAL_p3QVkuLb-_FKe_2SKiLMQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2.4 點Reg科</strong></span><br />\n講多無謂，睇片最實際。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ht35HgodlB4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHt35HgodlB4&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=1c2a434c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ht35HgodlB4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. Add Drop</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.1 咩係Add Drop？</span></strong><br />\n萬一reg唔齊cred點算<br />\n唔使驚，仲有add drop！<br />\nYr 1 Add drop嘅時間係最遲開始嘅。<br />\n今個sem應該係由9月6號開始。<br />\n你會被隨即編排到上晝或下晝嘅時段。<br />\n同樣，入Studies 》Registration 》Course Add/drop 睇翻所屬時段。<br />\n<br />\n如果大中、大英編排左個killer比你/唔啱時間，可以係pre reg嘅時段內改埋。<br />\n<br />\n試完堂覺得唔啱自己都可以利用呢add drop period drop科。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：每個course名額有限，未必一定搶到，祝君好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.2 Add唔到想讀嘅course點算？<br />\n冇辦法⋯⋯都未必嘅。<br />\n可以試下sit堂/email比lecturer求佢開多個位比你。<br />\n不過樓主呢啲個個sem都唔齊cred嘅可以話你知，成功機率極低。<br />\nVM只要你上宗哲系website，填左呢張form，基本上一定會開比你：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfVgzRX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfVgzRX.jpg&h=d589c8c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n宗哲系website：<a href=\"http://rel.hkbu.edu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frel.hkbu.edu.hk&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=1561ba0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://rel.hkbu.edu.hk</a><br />\nPE因為安全理由，人數限制好嚴格，唔使曬心機喇～<br />\n其他course就睇運氣啦。<br />\n<br />\n暫時講住咁多先，諗到再補充。"},{"pid":"bd6c8c4601fc90707a901157130237bdd8b698ea","tid":1430600,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:20:32.000Z","msg":"我要錫春袋"},{"pid":"47c528a5501066d08db08d5fb462c88219ce44b1","tid":1430600,"uid":63183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"今日唔係罷REG咩"},{"pid":"1d3b35cbf07e479a5f447e62558057209d4e9d3f","tid":1430600,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c528a5501066d08db08d5